As the mayor said at least one husband is a cheater. there are chances that there can be more than one husband cheating on their wife.
Assume only one husband is cheating, then his wife does not know about the cheater rest of the women know who the cheater is.
If two husbands are cheating then, those two husbands are killed.
similarly with three, four, and more.
For n number of cheaters, n husbands killed.


